sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Browser as admin-ui / tooling
    participant Agent as vending-pi ws_client
    participant SIO as Socket.IO Server socketio_gateway
    participant DB as MySQL machines

    rect rgb(230,240,255)
        Note over Browser,SIO: Admin dashboard
        Browser->>SIO: connect auth admin_token | role=admin
        SIO->>SIO: _verify_admin_auth
        SIO->>SIO: enter_room ADMIN_ROOM
    end

    rect rgb(255,240,230)
        Note over Agent,DB: Machine agent
        Agent->>SIO: connect auth machine_id + token
        SIO->>DB: bcrypt verify secret_token_hash
        SIO->>SIO: enter_room(machine_code)
        SIO->>DB: UPDATE is_online, last_active
    end
